2. Reynolds & Reynolds

Reynolds & Reynolds wants interns starting summer. The intern could 
possibly work through next year and they are interested in people who 
would be able to work in China possibly starting summer 2007. They are 
looking for individuals to be software testers, software developers and 
business analysts. Their most important first criteria is to be fluent 
in Mandarin.

All resumes relating to China are to be emailed directly to Connie 
Partridge at connie_partridge@reyrey.com.


